summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of $11.00, or so much thereof as may be necessary, from the General Fund of the City of Seattle for the purpose of paying the 1909 general taxes on the west 40 feet of the west half of the south one-half of the south one-half of the northwest one-quarter of the northeast one-quarter, and the west 40 feet of the west half of the southwest one-quarter of the northeast one-quarter in Section twenty-six (26), Township twenty-four (24) North, Range Three (3) East.
